  %% Diagram 40A: Security Controls Business-Friendly Journey

  User[User signs in]
  Verify[System verifies identity and permissions]
  Protect[System checks each request for safety rules]
  Decide{Request safe and allowed?}

  Allow[Action proceeds]
  Block[Action blocked]

  Payment[Payment callback verified and deduplicated]
  Escrow[Escrow release follows strict rules]
  Privacy[Data isolation protects each vendor]
  Audit[Every sensitive action is logged]

  User --> Verify --> Protect --> Decide
  Decide -- Yes --> Allow --> Payment --> Escrow --> Audit
  Decide -- No --> Block --> Audit

  Verify --> Privacy